				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2995e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            As part of the Homeland Security Act of 2002, Pub. L. 107-296, Congress enacted the SAFETY Act to-</p>
					          <ol id="d2981e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2995e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Encourage the development and use of anti-terrorism technologies that will enhance the protection of the nation; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2995e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Provide risk management and litigation management protections for sellers of QATTs and others in the supply and distribution chain.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2995e47" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
